sequenceDiagram
    participant Student as Student (browser)
    participant Manager as Manager
    participant Redis as Redis
    participant DB as Postgres
    participant Worker as Worker (selected)
    participant Clab as containerlab CLI

    Note over Worker,Manager: Worker connects at boot (or reconnect after crash)
    Worker->>Manager: ListenCommand() opens bidi stream
    Worker->>Manager: CommandPayload{workerSpec} (cpu/mem/storage, guacd host/port)
    Manager->>DB: upsert worker row, status=online
    Manager->>Worker: clab:reconcileSessions{activeSessionIds}
    Worker->>Worker: destroy any on-disk labs not in activeSessionIds
    Worker-->>Manager: destroyed lab ids

    Note over Student,Worker: Student starts a lab session
    Student->>Manager: WS RPC lab:[labId]:init
    Manager->>DB: tryGetAvailableWorkerId (SELECT ... FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED)
    alt no worker available
        Manager-->>Student: reply "warn": high demand, waiting...
        Manager->>Manager: waitForAvailableWorkerId (backoff loop)
    end
    Manager->>DB: insert lab_session row
    Manager->>Redis: dispatchWorkerAction("lab:initSession", workerId, payload)
    Redis-->>Manager: (same-replica: direct call; cross-replica: pubsub relay)
    Manager->>Worker: RPC clab:deployLab{sessionId, config}
    Worker->>Worker: buildTopology() -> LabConfig to Containerlab YAML
    Worker->>Clab: containerlab deploy --topo <path>
    Clab-->>Worker: deployed containers
    Worker->>Clab: containerlab inspect --details
    Clab-->>Worker: ContainerlabInspectNode[]
    Worker-->>Manager: DeployedNode[] {id, nodeId, ip, health}
    Manager->>DB: insert lab_session_node rows (+ guac tokens)
    Manager->>Manager: schedule BullMQ auto-submit job at dueDate
    Manager-->>Student: resolve deferred RPC reply {sessionId}

    Note over Worker,Manager: Ongoing: health + evaluator streaming
    Worker->>Manager: data monitor:node-health{id, health, lab}
    Manager->>DB: update lab_session_node.health
    Manager-->>Student: WS data node:[id]:health
    Worker->>Manager: data evaluator:checkChanged{sessionId, id, completed}
    Manager->>DB: upsert lab_session_check
    Manager-->>Student: WS data lab-session:[sessionId]:checks

    Note over Student,Worker: Session ends (manual submit or dueDate reached)
    Manager->>DB: compute weighted score, set submittedAt
    Manager->>Worker: RPC clab:destroyLab{sessionId}
    Worker->>Clab: containerlab destroy --keep-mgmt-net --cleanup
    Manager-->>Student: WS data lab-session:[sessionId]:ended
